      div
        p Born in Buenos Aires, Argentina, Florencia Mayer is a fashion jewelry designer specializing in artisanal techniques. She combines a unique ten year experience with a wide range of materials such as fresh pearls, recycled vintage pieces, rubber, and natural wools with an acute artistic taste. This ability allows her to create pieces that are more than just jewelry but are representations of the artist’s mind.
        p Her pursuit for the arts, have it be dancing flamenco and ballet or creating jewelry. She likes to innovate and try different materials, such us buttons, balloons. During her career Florencia created elegant collections for specialty shops and Museums in Argentina and Spain often inspired by historical and romantic imagery so vibrant in her culture. She made some gallery exhibition both in Buenos Aires as in Madrid.
