      h3 Materials
      p I have always been attracted to beautiful hand made pieces .
      p My passion for necklaces started by chance. When I began to create pieces and connect with the materials, I realized and understood the value of “creating” a new piece in connection with the person that would eventually wear it.
      p With my creations, I’m looking forward to awake the senses and generate a feeling of pleasure when wearing a piece.
      p My designs are mainly based on handy made forms creating ethereal sensations of movements through different textures and colours given by the materials I use (semiprecious stones, river pearls, mother of the pearls, passamanerie and organdy laces, and recycled antique jewelry.)
      p I have a passion for finding new materials and creating designs with them.
      p I´ve investigated and experimented with different materials, from buttons (galatit paste) to happy birthday balloons. I´ve arrived to the conclusion that I consider it important to appreciate our own natural resources and, on the other hand, create an environmental conscience besides thinking in their future sustenance.
        
